Round: Final (Aug 12 & 26)


Vasco da Gama            Bra  Barcelona                Ecu   2-0  2-1  4-1

1st leg. Rio de Janeiro, 12- 8-1998

Vasco da Gama - Barcelona 2-0
7' Donizete      1-0
35' Luizão        2-0

Vasco da Gama: Carlos Germano, Vagner (65' Vítor), Mauro Galvão, Odvan, Felipe, Luisinho, Nasa, Pedrinho (66' Ramon), Juninho, Donizete, Luizão
Barcelona: José Cevallos, Luis Gómez (37' Wagner Rivera), Jimmy Montanero, Holger Quiñonez, Luis Capurro, Julio Rosero (46' Héctor Carabalí), Macías (58' Fricson George), Marcelo Morales, Washington Aires, Nicolas Asencio, Anthony de Avila

2nd leg. Monumental Isidro Romero, Guayaquil, 26- 8-1998

Barcelona - Vasco da Gama 1-2
25' Luizão        0-1
45' Donizete      0-2
79' De Avila      1-2

Barcelona: José Cevallos, Jimmy Montanero, Raúl Noriega (46' Washington Aires), Holger Quiñonez, Luis Gómez, Marcelo Morales, Héctor Carabalí, Nicolas Asencio, Fricson George, Anthony de Avila, Agustín Delgado.
Vasco da Gama: Carlos Germano, Vagner, Odvan, Mauro Galvão, Felipe, Luisinho Nasa, Juninho, Pedrinho (75' Ramon), Donizete, Luizão (82' Alex).

Referee: Javier Castrilli (Argentina)
Attendance: 72,000


